<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk.Razor">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>net5.0</TargetFramework>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>true</PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>
    <Version>1.0.4</Version>
    <Authors>Sergi Ortiz Gomez</Authors>
    <Company>DrUalcman</Company>
    <Description>Component Blazor extend the normal InputFile with all the necessary to upload files. Also have a InputFileHandler can be inherit and add more functions</Description>
    <Copyright>Free</Copyright>
    <PackageLicenseFile>License.txt</PackageLicenseFile>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/drualcman/BlazorInputFileExtended</RepositoryUrl>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://blazorinputfileextended.community-mall.com/</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageTags>components, blazor, webassembly</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Control if have files selected when click on the button for upload files. If not fire a OnError Event.
Add property object TargetDataObject. Used to send all form data to the server. This create MultipartFormDataContent with the content about the object and send to the target post.
Add in InputFileHandler new UploadAsyc with 2 generic type TModel with the value must be return after send the files to the target post. And TData with the object content the form data the content to create <var>MultipartFormDataContent</var> with the Add methods update by FileId and remove by FileId or FileUploadContent object
content about the object and send to the target post.
Change property in FileUploadEventArgs from FileIndex to FileId.
In FileUploadContent ad properties FileId, FileBytes and ToImageHTML.
In InputFileExtended change OnSave return object to HttpResponseMessage
In InputFileHandler add Methods UploadAsync return HttpResponseMessage</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <RepositoryType>Component Library</RepositoryType>
    <PackageIcon>icon-512.png</PackageIcon>
    <PackageIconUrl />
    <AssemblyVersion>1.0.4.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>1.0.4.0</FileVersion>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='Debug|AnyCPU'">
    <DocumentationFile>C:\DrUalcman\BlazorInputFileExtended\BlazorInputFileExtended\BlazorInputFileExtended.xml</DocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Remove="icon-512.png" />
    <None Include="icon-512.png">
      <Pack>True</Pack>
      <PackagePath></PackagePath>
    </None>
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <Content Include="icon-512.png">
      <ExcludeFromSingleFile>true</ExcludeFromSingleFile>
      <CopyToPublishDirectory>PreserveNewest</CopyToPublishDirectory>
    </Content>
  </ItemGroup>

  
  <ItemGroup>
    <SupportedPlatform Include="browser" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.Web" Version="5.0.7" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="License.txt">
      <Pack>True</Pack>
      <PackagePath></PackagePath>
    </None>
  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
